      "text": "Why do we sweat?"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 14960.0,
      "end_time": 18000.0,
      "text": "It is a natural way of our body to take a\nbath."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 18600.0,
